{"tid":2309350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"博科聖地血洗奈及利亞村莊 至少有110名農民遭割喉","createTime":"2020-12-02T13:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T17:43:15.000Z","uid":295230,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1033e7356d8193593e1a96a9226e067d3b767b3c","tid":2309350,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:05:08.000Z","msg":"28日早上，奈及利亞東北部博爾諾州（Borno）最大城市邁杜古里（Maiduguri）附近的科舒貝村（Koshobe），慘遭極端組織「博科聖地」（Boko Haram）血洗，導致多人死亡。聯合國估計，隨著搜尋行動的展開，死亡人數可能上升至110人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/83HoUCX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F83HoUCX.jpg&h=bc2056f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，這起發生在科舒貝村的恐怖襲擊，主要針對當地正在處理農務工作的農民。州長祖盧姆（Babagana Zulum）證實，遇害的村民是在農田幹活時遭到襲擊，這些可憐的農夫被冷血的恐怖分子割喉，當場慘死。<br />\n<br />\n奈及利亞當局暫時只找到了43具屍體，但聯合國估計，隨著搜尋行動的展開，死亡人數可能上升至110人，「是奈及利亞年內爆發的最慘恐攻」。聯合國人道主義協調員卡隆（Edward Kallon）表示，他對於平民受到「直接的暴力襲擊感到憤怒和恐懼」。<br />\n<br />\n而奈及利亞總統布哈里（Muhammadu Buhari）也發表聲明指出，博科聖地的暴行已讓「整個奈及利亞都受到傷害」，聯邦政府將向武裝部隊提供必要的支持，以加強打擊該極端組織的力度。<br />\n<br />\n有著奈及利亞「塔利班」之稱的博科聖地是一個伊斯蘭教組織，其目標是主張在奈及利亞全國推行穆罕默德先知的伊斯蘭教法，以及透過聖戰，成為哈里發國的一部份。該組織成立十餘年來，頻繁出沒於奈及利亞東北部，並對周邊的多個國家構成了安全威脅。"},{"pid":"4127a4442d29224dbc9f2b3c512f4b608bf64b53","tid":2309350,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:07:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/nov/29/nigeria-attack-boko-haram-farm-workers-killed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2020%2Fnov%2F29%2Fnigeria-attack-boko-haram-farm-workers-killed&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=d9a6ad96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/nov/29/nigeria-attack-boko-haram-farm-workers-killed</a>"},{"pid":"92ad31bc3c71568955f92ce55cd5c723ceae52df","tid":2309350,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55a6189144704b418f94139f31d63639c48db89","tid":2309350,"uid":3873,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭教法教你屠殺平民架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d060779d4bc31c3d9d4789f20720aa30adb0d3a","tid":2309350,"uid":55533,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:14:37.000Z","msg":"blm又集體失明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd66d067922f0c216f01572abaf115555b11981c","tid":2309350,"uid":295230,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"c55a6189144704b418f94139f31d63639c48db89","tid":2309350,"uid":3873,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭教法教你屠殺平民架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:14:45.000Z","msg":"宗教法不嬲都係當權力者自己演繹，有咩反對就推個神出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae92070ff8564de3cd2e4ece1ecadd088110cd9c","tid":2309350,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c55a6189144704b418f94139f31d63639c48db89","tid":2309350,"uid":3873,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭教法教你屠殺平民架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:16:20.000Z","msg":"勉強可以用大小聖戰概念去諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c74fe5df36fd6fb58bdca6422de2a28fe11f135","tid":2309350,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:16:31.000Z","msg":"香港人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e296e78f4012b9df1d3a78bb8d8fe324f389a9f5","tid":2309350,"uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c55a